{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Wood Snake|kanji=乙巳|romaji=kinoto mi|onyomi=otsushi|p=yǐsì|w=i-ssu|mi=i²¹ sɨ|y=jyut6 si6|j=jyut6 si6|ci=jyt̚ siː|mc=ʔit si|oc-bs=Ɂik si|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Wood Snake also known as Yin Wood Snake''' (乙巳, Kinoto-Mi, Otsuboku-no-Mi, Isshi) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
It is the 42nd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Jiachen|ja|甲辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Bingwu|ja|丙午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Five Elements|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} character {{ill|Yi|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Wood (wuxing)|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} character {{ill|Si|ja|巳|1=Snake (zodiac)|lt=Snake (巳)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Fire (wuxing)|ja|火|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, forming a generating ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) relationship (Wood generates Fire).
== Yin Wood Snake Years == Years where the remainder when divided by 60 is 45 are Yin Wood Snake years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Wood Snake Years''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | *[[45]] *[[105]] *[[165]] *[[225]] *[[285]] *[[345]] *[[405]] *[[465]] *[[525]] *[[585]] *[[645]] *[[705]] *[[765]] *[[825]] *[[885]] *[[945]] | *[[1005]] *[[1065]] *[[1125]] *[[1185]] *[[1245]] *[[1305]] *[[1365]] *[[1425]] *[[1485]] *[[1545]] *[[1605]] *[[1665]] *[[1725]] *[[1785]] *[[1845]] *[[1905]] *[[1965]] | *[[2025]] *[[2085]] *[[2145]] *[[2205]] *[[2265]] *[[2325]] *[[2385]] *[[2445]] *[[2505]] *[[2565]] *[[2625]] *[[2685]] *[[2745]] *[[2805]] *[[2865]] *[[2925]] *[[2985]] |}
=== Events === * The downfall of the Soga clan by {{ill|Prince Naka no Ōe|ja|中大兄皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and {{ill|Nakatomi no Kamatari|ja|中臣鎌足|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} in [[645]] is known as the {{ill|Isshi Incident|ja|乙巳の変|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. * The {{ill|Eulsa Treaty|ja|第二次日韓協約|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} signed in [[1905]] is referred to as the '''Eulsa''' Protection Treaty in Korea.
== Yin Wood Snake Months == April of years ending in 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) corresponds to the Yin Wood Snake {{ill|Month|ja|月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, in the case of traditional calendars, the Yin Wood Snake month may be applied based on the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lixia|ja|立夏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}).
== Yin Wood Snake Days ==
=== Special Calendar Notations === * Yin Wood Snake day is the 13th day of the {{ill|Tianyi Tian Shang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} cycle. == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} * {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} * {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}
