It is the 42nd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Jiachen|ja|甲辰|1=Yang Wood Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiachen|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Bingwu|ja|丙午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bingwu|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Five Elements|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Five Elements|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} character {{ill|Yi|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Wood (wuxing)|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} character {{ill|Si|ja|巳|1=Snake (zodiac)|lt=Snake (巳)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Si|13=User:Immanuelle/Snake (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Fire (wuxing)|ja|火|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire (wuxing)|qq=}}, forming a generating ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) relationship (Wood generates Fire).
