=== Events === * The downfall of the Soga clan by {{ill|Prince Naka no Ōe|ja|中大兄皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Naka no Ōe|qq=}} and {{ill|Nakatomi no Kamatari|ja|中臣鎌足|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakatomi no Kamatari|qq=}} in [[645]] is known as the {{ill|Isshi Incident|ja|乙巳の変|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isshi Incident|qq=}}. * The {{ill|Eulsa Treaty|ja|第二次日韓協約|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eulsa Treaty|qq=}} signed in [[1905]] is referred to as the '''Eulsa''' Protection Treaty in Korea.
== Yin Wood Snake Months == April of years ending in 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}) corresponds to the Yin Wood Snake {{ill|Month|ja|月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Month|qq=}}. However, in the case of traditional calendars, the Yin Wood Snake month may be applied based on the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lixia|ja|立夏|1=Lixia|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lixia|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mangzhong|qq=}}).
== Yin Wood Snake Days ==
=== Special Calendar Notations === * Yin Wood Snake day is the 13th day of the {{ill|Tianyi Tian Shang|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tianyi Tian Shang|qq=}} cycle. == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}} * {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} * {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}
